    'l10n.expansion': 'String expansion',
    'l10n.expansionDesc': 'The same label is a different length in every language — German runs ~35% longer, Chinese shorter. Never fix a control’s width to its English label; set a min-width and let it grow.',
    'l10n.bidi': 'Bidirectional & CJK',
    'l10n.bidiDesc': 'Switching to a right-to-left language mirrors the whole layout — icon side, alignment and padding flip via antd direction. The CJK fallback font is already in the type token.',
    'l10n.format': 'Number, date & currency',
    'l10n.formatDesc': 'antd ConfigProvider locale drives pickers, pagination and empty states; values you format yourself use Intl. Below, one instant and one number rendered per locale — adapting to ISO 8601 (numeric, 24h), the EU order, the US 12-hour clock and the Chinese 年月日 form.',
