    'vlist.note': 'antd 6 Table windows rows with the virtual prop (rc-virtual-list): only the visible slice plus a small buffer is in the DOM, so 10,000 rows scroll as smoothly as 20. The live counter proves it — flip virtual off and the same data (capped to 400 here so it can’t hang) mounts every row. Virtualization is a render optimisation, not a data-fetch strategy: for truly huge sets, paginate on the server.',
